author: varia
title: Dywan
body: W poniedziałek Krajowa Rada Radiofonii i Telewizji zdecydowała o przedłużeniu koncesji dla TVN24. Przed głosowaniem KRRiT podjęła uchwałę, która jak przekazała rzecznika podczas spotkania, była niezbędna dla podjęcia decyzji. Dojdzie do przekazania dokumentów.

author: varia
title: Lviv Theatre of Opera and Ballet
body:
Two photos of the Lviv Theatre of Opera and Ballet taken in June 2016 during one-day trip. I highly recommend this city. I feel I could walk over a month through this City and it would still be undiscovered...

![IMG_6766.JPG](https://steemitimages.com/DQme4jVzyT3iSiFJD8cHiQXcXD5KeaUNzsvLhdYmaKJM19U/IMG_6766.JPG)

BTW, ticket for the opera is very cheap. I recommend taking this into account when you will go to Lviv.

![IMG_6770.JPG](https://steemitimages.com/DQmRevAftCui1Rem2cTBmu6bDPfvhqSioR3KZ2nJMCaF4vg/IMG_6770.JPG)
root_title: Lviv Theatre of Opera and Ballet

author: varia
title: Old Warsaw
body:
Before WWII Warsaw was called "Paris of the North". During the war, especially during the Uprising 1944, the city was totally destroyed. Despite the reconstruction Old Warsaw has gone forever...

Below are pictures from 1890.

<center>

![wawa.jpg](https://steemitimages.com/DQmeToRYwoKvPMLHaoAi5L9pK6Kv653NQBzGUaZxbrS1gYu/wawa.jpg)

King Sigismund's monument

![wawa2.jpg](https://steemitimages.com/DQmX4wp6s3e28tJcabp6myc4JMAwfVDx6Pgu4V62pfDgcgb/wawa2.jpg)

Grand theatre

![wawa3.jpg](https://steemitimages.com/DQmWxcwG99YQqWktZYiBZUwFoahUGX9LCKxtGf5TbK3HQdR/wawa3.jpg)

Town hall.

![wawa4.jpg](https://steemitimages.com/DQmbZc4ivQYUXUc95ZPZfThjQaRXWp7Vec4WyzXQ34finwX/wawa4.jpg)

St. Anna's Church

![wawa5.jpg](https://steemitimages.com/DQmauwwKMqeijnWwuQ4iaxLzQNqB3iJkALgsWbgPFefDgdi/wawa5.jpg)

author: varia
title: Bima
body:
On November 8th, 1939, the Old Synagogue in Tarnów was destroyed by the Germans and later demolished; all that remains today is the brick 'bimah' - a four-pillared podium from which the Torah was read.
***
#### [View in VR @ dlux.io](https://dlux.io/dlux/@varia/bima)

author: varia
title: Galician town
body:
![rts2.jpg](https://cdn.steemitimages.com/DQmU4zV9f4M3WNRJW3vU9uSCfYEW3n8nxTixWF2VfM4zDdM/rts2.jpg)

I like this picture. A typical Galician town. The final period of the Austro-Hungarian Empire. The Poles are standing on the street leading to Lviv. There is no war yet, but independence is near...
